    <div class="lr-faq-list">
      <div class="lr-faq-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          What's included in the pricing?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>All pricing includes senior engineers, project management, code reviews, testing, documentation, and deployment. You get a complete team, not just developers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-faq-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          Do you offer hourly rates?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>We prefer weekly or monthly engagements for better consistency and results. Hourly work doesn't align with our AI-native approach where we ship features, not hours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-faq-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          What if my project needs change?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>For Time & Materials, you have full flexibility. For Project-Based, we handle scope changes through transparent change requests. We'll never surprise you with extra costs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-faq-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          Can I hire just one engineer?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>Yes, our Time & Materials model allows you to start with a single senior engineer. As your needs grow, we can scale up the team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-faq-item">
        <button class="lr-faq-question">
          What's your cancellation policy?
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lr-faq-answer">
          <p>Time & Materials engagements can be cancelled with 2 weeks notice. Project-Based contracts have milestone-based payment terms. We believe in earning your trust, not locking you in.</p>
